cs.SE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.PL 

Reasoning: 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category as the paper is focused on predicting the time to build software and assisting in the management and control of software development. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes the use of a hybrid system based on artificial neural networks and fuzzy systems. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses artificial neural networks for prediction. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses the management and control of software development. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the complexity of the system to be developed and how it affects the time necessary for completion.
